    "content": "## Aider\n- Added GPT-5, Grok-4, gemini/gemini-flash-lite support, /clear output, /undo output, openrouter/moonshotai/kimi-k2 support, display model announcements\n## OpenAI SDK\n- Custom voices, API update, Sora API improvements, merged videos resource repair, GA ComputerTool, gpt-5.4, tool search, new computer tool, remove prompt_cache_key, phase field from message types, internal schema fixes, readd phase, add phase, fix phase enum, gpt-realtime, gpt-audio, websockets for responses API, container network_policy, skills, images in batch API, hosted shell\n## Hugging Face\n- NeMo Retriever, Storage Buckets, RL Libraries lessons, Granite Speech\n## Anthropic SDK\n- Clean up model enum, GA thinking-display-setting, add 413 and 529 error handlers, propagate container_id, use filtered messages list, change array_format, remove publishing section, add conversion helpers, add missing raw jsonl results, add top-level cache control, fix UserLocation and error code types, add backward-compat aliases, make new tool versions available, release claude-sonnet, fix spec errors, remove speed, enable fast-mode in claude-opus, pass speed parameter, release Claude Opus, adaptive thinking, send structured output beta header, add structured outputs, migrate sending message format, add custom JSON encoder, use output_config for structured outputs, remove class causing breaking change\n## Ollama\n- Improved OpenClaw performance with Kimi-K2.5, tool calling accuracy improved, now a provider in OpenClaw, decompress zstd request bodies, close thinking block, populate ollama ls, repair unclosed arg_value tags, don't require pulling stubs, fix localhost handling, smarter docker parallelism, int4 groupsize, handle stream disconnects, replace sampler interface, fix missing windows zip file, MLX perf improvements, fix windows build, add header vendoring, remove go build tag, allow thinking levels, add context length\n## Claude Code\n- Added MCP elicitation, Elicitation and ElicitationResult hooks, -n / --name CLI flag, worktree.sparsePaths setting, PostCo, pass confirmed=true, actionable suggestions to /context, autoMemoryDirectory setting, fixed memory leak, fixed managed policy ask rules, modelOverrides setting, actionable guidance, fixed freezes, fixed a deadlock, changed tool search, added w key in /copy, added optional description to /plan, added claude plugins alias, ExitWorktree tool, /loop command, cron scheduling tools, voice:pushToTalk keybinding, added bash auto-approval allowlist, fixed stdin, fixed API 400 errors, fixed API Error, fixed empty model responses, added /claude-api skill, Ctrl+U on empty bash prompt, numeric keypad support, optional name to /remote-control, Opus defaults to medium effort, re-introduced \"ultrathink\", removed Opus and\n## Latent Space\n- Context Drought, high-return activity of raising your aspirations for LLMs, Retrieval After RAG, Replit Agent, Yann LeCun\u2019s AMI Labs, NVIDIA's AI Engineers, Autoresearch\n## Last Week in AI\n- Nemotron Super, xAI reborn, Anthropic Lawsuit, Research!, Anthropic sues Trump, xAI starting over, Iran AI Fakes, GPT , Gemini Flash Lite, Supply Chain Risk\n## Gemini CLI\n- Changelog for v, update theme screenshots, add missing themes, rename 'return' key to 'enter', restrict npm bundling, override toolRegistry, make footer items equally spaced, clarify global policy rules application, cherry-pick 24adacd, cherry-pick 8432bce, cherry-pick 45faf4d, add chat resume footer, support bold and other styles, increase A2A agent timeout, cleanup old branches, bump version to nightly, standardize semantic focus colors, enhance history visibility, merge dupl, update model docs, fix typo, add Windows PowerShell equivalents, parse raw ASCII buffer strings, use robot PAT, cherry-pick 3ff68a9, whitelist TERM and COLORTERM, fix overage strategy lifecycle, expand paste placeholders, add in-memory cache, overhaul thinking UI, unify Ctrl+O expansion hint"
  }
